NCID Source package:                     ncid-0.72-src.tar.gz

NCID Binary Packages:

    Fedora package:                      ncid-0.72-1.fc9.i386.rpm
    Fedora 64 bit package:               ncid-0.72-1.fc9.x86_64.rpm
    TiVo Series1 package:                ncid-0.72-1-ppc-tivo.tgz
    TiVo Series 2 and 3 package:         ncid-0.72-1-mips-tivo.tgz
    Macintosh OS X (i386 & ppc) package: ncid-0.72-1-mac-osx.tgz
    FreeBSD 5.4 package:                 ncid-0.72-1-freebsd.tgz
    Cygwin Windows package:              ncid-0.72-1-cygwin.tgz
    Windows client installer:            ncid-0.72-1-client_setup.exe
    Ubuntu package:                      ncid_0.72-0ubuntu1_i386.deb

Specific distribution Changes:

    Fedora:
        Updated ncidd.init, sip2ncid.init, ncidsip.init

        The Fedora binary distribution can be built for particular Fedora
        and Redhat releases by rebuilding the package:

            rpmbuild -tb ncid-0.72-src.tar.gz

    FreeBSD:
        Updated ncidd.rc, sip2ncid.rc, ncidsip.rc

    Mac OS-X:

    Ubuntu:
        Updated ncidd.init, sip2ncid.init, ncidsip.init

    TiVo:
        Added the startncid script to easily start NCID.
        The script sets the local timezone for the Gateways.
        The script must be reviewed and modified before use.

NCID Server Changes:

    ncidd:
        Modified to allow a optional pid file

    ncidd.conf:
        Added a Mac OSX init string as a comment.

NCID Gateway Changes:

    sip2ncid:
        Fixed a overflow on large sip packets.
        Fixed some possible logic problems.
        Modified to run on a TiVo series 1
        Modified to allow a optional pid file

    ncidsip:
        Modified to allow a optional pid file

    yac2ncid:
        Changed test for broken bash on the TiVo.

NCID Client Changes:

    ncid:
        Modified telephone number format to handle two countries: US and SE
        Changed the display separaters for telephone numbers.
        Fixed a startup problem on the TiVo.
        Added simple X11 detection to go into GUI mode.
        Added color to the displayed GUI text.
        Changed Message display, moved from GUI history window to call label

NCID Client Module Changes:

    ncidmodules.conf:
        Updated comments on ncid-page

Documentation Changes:

    Corrected a error in ncidtools.1
    Updated sip2ncid.8, ncidd.8, ncidsip.8, ncid.1
    Added CountryCodes to list country codes that the ncid display supports
